\begin_inset Formula $\mu<\mu_{c2}$
\end_inset

.
 In addition, the authors applied the optimal control theory to obtain an
 optimal vaccination strategy 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu*(t)$
\end_inset

 and gave some numerical simulations for those theoretical findings.
 Finally, they used the model SEIR to simulate the data of measles cases
 in the U.S.
